 type $B$\nanalogues of our constructions. Notably, we define a partial order that\ngeneralizes the type $B$ Tamari lattice, introduced independently by Thomas and\nReading, along with corresponding geometric realizations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2016 19:16:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Oct 2017 15:47:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-12"}
