ation (LOOCV) scheme with 96.88%\nsensitivity, 100% specificity and 98.44% accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2016 20:36:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-30"}
