edge of PBH formation. These, and other effects, such as merging,\nclustering and accretion, may also loosen constraints from non-observations of\nother primordial compact objects such as ultra-compact minihalos of dark\nmatter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2016 09:59:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2017 13:08:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2017 14:24:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 2 Feb 2018 16:23:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-06"}
